data.title: Luggage Storage Copenhagen Svanemøllen Railway Station
data.meta_description: Book now online your luggage storage in Copenhagen,Svanemøllen Railway Station with Radical Storage. The staff is available to keep your baggage, only €5.0/day.
data.text: Although our QR code was not scanned and we didn't get any receipt as proof that we stored the luggage, we got it back 2 weeks later without any issues. The location was great as well as the opening hours. So it is recommended. I do suggest to attach a name tag.
